he will go down soon after WS runs out but not that soon if you even try to keep him alive.<br>
<br>
if that does not give you enough time to kill him (basicaly burn on him with lures) :<br>
<br>
no SK / Pally taunt (since they don´t have riposte discs)<br>
<br>
when Ranger goes down, keep ready to hit riposte as soon as you get agro.<br>
<br>
those who get agro are lost anyway so just riposte him to death to give everyone else a few more seconds to unleash their fury on him.<br>
<br>
